@wp.kernel
def expr_bxujro(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    tmp = v1
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.51) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.99)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.55 * tmp + 0.32)))
    tmp = 0.04
    v1 = v2
    v2 = 0.58
    data[tid] = v0
